---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>About Us</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold my-8">About Us</h1>
  <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg">
    We are a leading rice factory committed to delivering the highest quality rice to households and businesses worldwide. Our mission is to provide healthy, organic, and sustainable rice that meets the diverse needs of our customers.
  </p>
  <BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn more about our rice factory and mission.">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-7">
      We are a leading rice factory committed to producing the finest quality rice for homes and businesses around the world. Our mission is to
      deliver organic, sustainable rice while supporting local farmers and ensuring the highest standards of quality in every grain.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-7">
      Founded in 1990, we have been at the forefront of innovation in rice milling and distribution, combining traditional methods with modern
      technology to produce rice that is not only delicious but also eco-friendly.
    </p>
  </BaseLayout>
</body>
</html>
